## ❓ Frequently Asked Questions

### **General Questions**

**Q: Is my data private?**  
A: Yes! All your data is stored locally on your device. We don't collect, store, or transmit any personal information to external servers.

**Q: Do I need an account?**  
A: No. Anchor Me works completely offline without requiring any account or login.

**Q: Does the app require an internet connection?**  
A: No. All features work offline. Internet is only needed for in-app purchases.

### **Subscription Questions**

**Q: What's included in the premium subscription?**  
A: Premium unlocks unlimited access to all breathing exercises, grounding techniques, and session history tracking.

**Q: How do I cancel my subscription?**  
A: Subscriptions are managed through your Apple ID. Go to Settings → [Your Name] → Subscriptions → Anchor Me → Cancel Subscription.

**Q: Can I get a refund?**  
A: Refund requests are handled by Apple. Visit [reportaproblem.apple.com](https://reportaproblem.apple.com) to request a refund.

**Q: What's the difference between subscription tiers?**
- **Monthly:** €4.99/month - Full access, cancel anytime
- **Annual:** €49.99/year - Full access with 3-day free trial (save 17%)
- **Lifetime:** €129.99 one-time - Full access forever, no recurring payments

### **Technical Questions**

**Q: The app isn't working after an iOS update. What should I do?**  
A: Try these steps:
1. Force quit the app (swipe up from app switcher)
2. Restart your iPhone
3. Check for app updates in the App Store
4. If issues persist, email us at anchorsupportme@proton.me

**Q: Can I sync data between devices?**  
A: Currently, data is stored locally on each device. Cloud sync may be added in future updates.

**Q: How do I restore my purchase?**  
A: Go to Settings → Subscription → Restore Purchases. This will restore any active subscriptions or lifetime purchases tied to your Apple ID.

